{"tid":1717912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再咁落去真系含撚 [長文慎入]","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:53:49.000Z","uid":300558,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"04017c555254f26702ec1da1753c35433e1fa685","tid":1717912,"uid":300558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱先同藍絲老母辯論完，有咁而發想講少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <strong>戴頭盔先第一次開po有錯勿屌</strong><br />\n首先系召喚神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本豬好<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔支持</span>神獸，但系只要藍絲一郁手，自衛都唔係好過分姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">但個前提系佢有郁手咯</span><br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 影出黎畫面唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 點同人文宣/ 解話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都話香港受國際關注，但系咁既畫面出到國際，真系好難唔引人誤會覺得我地濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然過左咁多個月，大家都好嬲好大壓力，但系佢邊撚個姐，佢得把口既咪由得佢鳩up 下咯。<span style=\"color: gold;\">我真系好唔鐘意神獸咯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二係裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵美心旗下同360 就自然可以隨便<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫襯</span>啦，但系如果比人見到普通藍店都比人搞，真係好難比人認同咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地藍屍裝修我地黃店唔代表我地要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋火魔真系唔好隨便放，搞到民居燒到隔離真系兜唔到，手足你地實有辦法用其他工具裝修既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地睇下班藍屍一比防暴屌兩句/ 射tg 點撚樣？你就會明民意幾容易逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講都口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都系加油感化下身邊既藍絲中立撚啦，再叫埋身邊既人一齊出去發夢，前線街坊FA文宣咩都好，多佢一個真系好多，前線真系唔夠人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都出黎發聲淋病會唔知點算架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經第六個月，大家都好撚攰，負面情緒爆曬出黎，但系唔好唔記得，我地用既雖然都系武力，但系我地同個殺人政權最大既分別就系我地有信念，我地有目標，我地有理性。我地應該憤怒，但系唔可以比憤怒掩蓋雙眼，更加唔可以比佢打到屈服！都系嗰句： 光復香港 時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022408fe9a9175d609b2753f6861741ba8f55b9a","tid":1717912,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712e43992edc1800303bb3f76f5f6db97e47973","tid":1717912,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6eb8b621cece671ff3da97f020dba539aeffb1","tid":1717912,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1714238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1714238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a01cb705a7139a4311e24caec1336f26556bc9e9","tid":1717912,"uid":135110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"系你老尾"},{"pid":"9f08a9d8bfeceb31681c9fac523ddf3a5730d7c7","tid":1717912,"uid":331822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"1 就都基本認同<br />\n2就唔太認同，我只係認為文宣追唔切係呢幾日入面"},{"pid":"27022